Project Proposal 

Our teams Idea was to do a Top-Down Shooter that represents parallel and distributed processes. We have yet to name the game for reference; we call it TDS. TDS is aimed at demonstrating the concepts of how workloads can be divided and optimized using mutli threading, while comparing strong and weak scaling systems in a real time environment.  

